RESEARCH DISCLAIMER

This software is developed strictly for academic and research purposes.
It is not a certified agricultural advisory system and must not be used
as the sole basis for any agronomic decision in commercial settings.
All outputs — including disease classifications, treatment plans, and
reasoning traces — should be reviewed and validated by a qualified
agronomist or plant pathologist before operational use.

The training dataset (PlantVillage) is subject to its own terms of use.
This software may not be redistributed with the dataset without complying
with those terms.
